parameters:
??? 'It's rare for Armada to have guests. I wonder who
these young ladies are?'

Noble Orikuto: I should introduce myself first. I am
Orikuto, a noble from Valier.

Adventurer Armada: Do you have any business with my
companions, Orikuto?

Noble Orikuto: Companion, huh... So you've finally arrived
at your destination.

Adventurer Armada: If someone hadn't been causing trouble,
we might have gathered sooner.

Adventurer Armada: Thanks to you, I was able to meet the
best companions. I sincerely appreciate that, Orikuto.

Noble Orikuto: Why am I not good enough!? I have prepared
funds and personnel to support you!

Adventurer Armada: Let me make it simple, Orikuto. I seek
adventure, while you seek honor.
Adventurer Armada: Now, please go back.

Noble Orikuto: Hmph, these young ladies are also going away
from you. You wouldn't want them to meet an unfortunate
fate, would you?

Clea: I am an adventurer belonging to the Adventurer's
Guild, Ftera branch. I will fulfill any request from Armada-
san, no matter what it may be.

Noble Orikuto: The Adventurer's Guild...! Wasn't Agonia at
odds with them?!

Mage Relm: I would be troubled if you forgot about me! The
great genius of the Magic Academy is also here!

Priestess Sophia: Oh, do we need introductions? I am a
priestess of the Terios Church, hikku!
Thief Nora: Um... well... I, um, am a thief...

Noble Orikuto: They are quite interesting companions.
Alright, I will also seriously support and cooperate with
them!

Adventurer Armada: I'm sorry, I didn't mean to make you
feel bad.
Clea: It's okay, please don't worry.

Adventurer Armada: I'm not a bad person, it's just that my
methods are a bit... well, I'll explain someday.

Adventurer Armada: I'm going to be very busy from now on!
Once the investigation is done, I'll directly request a
mission from the guild.
実績 探検家アルマダ、夢の入口

Miner Man: Have you met Armada? She is the treasure of
Valier, the pride of this village!

Miner Man: Have you met Armada? She is the treasure of
Valier, the pride of this village!

Meddlesome Auntie: I wish a woman as amazing as Armada
would pursue her own happiness instead of remaining single.

Meddlesome Auntie: I wish a woman as amazing as Armada
would pursue her own happiness instead of remaining single.

Traveling Merchant: I love this village, even though I sell
my wares all over! It somehow feels more lively and vibrant
than other places.

Traveling Merchant: I love this village, even though I sell
my wares all over! It just has a different kind of energy
that makes it lively.

Miner Man: Armada was lovely today... I just hope she
doesn't receive any harassment from Ect... I'm worried...

Miner Man: Armada was lovely today... I just hope she
doesn't receive any harassment from Ect... I'm worried...

Thief Nora: Armada-san... You were clearly feeling down,
weren't you?

Priestess Sophia: It's unbearable to be just one step away
from a lifelong dream and not have any clues.
Priestess Phoni: Is there anything I can do?

Mage Relm: As a fellow researcher, I can assert that
amateurs should not meddle with it.

Clea: We should believe in Armada-san, we will definitely
find her.

Chronos Thief Leader Gift: It seems that Armada is at a
dead end.

Chronos Thief Leader Gift: I will go report. You must
definitely deliver this request letter.

Chronos Thief Leader Gift: Take it to the Adventurer's
Guild.

events.name: クロノス盗賊団団長ギフト

parameters:
Thief Nora: I hear a voice... a voice that seems to be in
agony!
Clea: Let's go inside. There might be something happening.

Adventurer Armada: What are you doing here? If it's about
the progress of the book, I'd appreciate it if you could
wait a little longer.

Noble Ect: You're really terrible at organizing documents!
I can't even tell which documents should be brought into the
mansion!

Noble Ect: Oh my, excuse me... Is there something you want
us to investigate?
Thief Nora: Um, it's hard to say, but...

Storge of Benevolence: Let me explain the rest. I stopped
by while on a mission from Agonia.

Adventurer Armada: Are you here to request something that
even the prominent figures of the Adventurer's Guild find
challenging?
Noble Ect: I absolutely absolutely absolutely oppose it!

Adventurer Armada: Hey hey, my eardrums are going to
burst... Ect.

Noble Ect: It's reckless to go against the Caron regime
itself! You finally obtained the days of research you
desired, didn't you!?

Noble Ect: You wouldn't do something as foolish as throwing
it away, would you!?

Adventurer Armada: My answer has been decided from the
beginning.

Noble Ect: If that's the case, then it's good. I think you
all will understand--

Adventurer Armada: So, when is the scheduled date for the
operation?

Clea: Once the exact date and time is decided, I intend to
inform you again.

Adventurer Armada: Since my body has become dull, I'll have
to say goodbye to the desk and pen for a while and train
again.

Noble Ect: Why, Armada... I am your research partner, I
want you to explain.

Adventurer Armada: It's because I can conduct research with
you. That's why they fought risking their lives, repaying
the reward.

Adventurer Armada: Friends who chased after dreams together
came to me, bowing their heads, to ask for a favor.

Adventurer Armada: Next, it's my turn to risk my life. I'll
finish it quickly and come back, so don't worry!
Noble Ect: ...I understand, I agree with that.

Noble Ect: However, please explain about this man! Who
exactly is he? He seems quite familiar with you!

Thief Nora: Oh, please don't get angry! We're old
acquaintances, um, we're close friends, um...
Noble Ect: So he's your ex-boyfriend...!

Storge of Benevolence Nora, please don't complicate things
and make the conversation difficult...

Thief Nora: I-I'm sorry! Um, well, it's like, we're not
lovers, but we're close!

Noble Ect: So he's more than a friend but less than a
lover...!

Adventurer Armada: Ahahaha, let's finish everything and
have another silly conversation.

Adventurer Armada: I'm not particularly religious, but I'm
grateful to the Three Goddesses for giving me the
opportunity to repay my debts.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
